> **Warning**
>
> This project is very-very-very new and will change significantly.
> If I was you, **I wouldn't use it**.

## Installation

Install with `pipx`.

```shell
pipx install pydistcheck
```

## Minimal Example

Given a Python distribution...

```shell
pydistcheck dist/*.tar.gz
```

